  "description": "P39 phosphor afterglow at the lowest usable brightness — a held note that doesn't know it should have faded. Pulse rate minimal, feedback just above the decay floor. The sound is the color of a terminal screen at 2am: green, patient, inevitable. Foundation-tier: OPTIC at its simplest and most honest.",
